# Build artifacts (recreated inside the image)
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.next
**/.turbo
**/coverage
**/*.tsbuildinfo

# Local env files (secrets are injected by the host)
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# VCS / editor / OS noise
.git
.github
.vscode
.idea
.DS_Store

# Repo-level docs and tests aren't needed at runtime
docs
*.md
!apps/api/README.md
